{"id":301,"ayahs":[{"number":62,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا جَاوَزَا قَالَ لِفَتَىٰهُ ءَاتِنَا غَدَآءَنَا لَقَدْ لَقِينَا مِن سَفَرِنَا هَٰذَا نَصَبًۭا","translation":"And after the two had walked some distance, [Moses] said to his servant: \"Bring us our mid-day meal; we have indeed suffered hardship on this [day of] our journey!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2202.mp3","surahId":18,"words":[{"id":55560,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55561,"position":2,"arabic":"جَاوَزَا","translation":"দু'জনে অতিক্রম করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55562,"position":3,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55563,"position":4,"arabic":"لِفَتَىٰهُ","translation":"তার যুবক (সেবক)-কে","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55564,"position":5,"arabic":"ءَاتِنَا","translation":"\"আমাদেরকে দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55565,"position":6,"arabic":"غَدَآءَنَا","translation":"আমাদের (নাশতা) খাবার","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55566,"position":7,"arabic":"لَقَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55567,"position":8,"arabic":"لَقِينَا","translation":"আমরা পেয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55568,"position":9,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55569,"position":10,"arabic":"سَفَرِنَا","translation":"আমাদের ভ্রমণ","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55570,"position":11,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","translation":"এই","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55571,"position":12,"arabic":"نَصَبًۭا","translation":"ক্লান্তি\"","audioUrl":"wbw/018_062_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":55572,"position":13,"ar